        <h2 class="faq-headline">What they always ask us</h2>

        <div class="faq-list">

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Do I need a big investment to start dropshipping?<svg class="faq-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
            <p class="faq-body">Droparabia's main purpose allows you to start your dropshipping or ecommerce business with a tiny budget of $500 minimum without wasting your money on bulk inventories that might not sell, renting warehouses or paying for shipment and import fees.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Does dropshipping actually work in Lebanon?<svg class="faq-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
            <p class="faq-body">When lots of people on the internet were saying that "Dropshipping is dead" or "doesn't work in any arab country", they meant the old dropshipping model where you have to gamble with your money on products hoping they might sell while paying huge fees. With Droparabia however, the game has changed. Now all you need is a small budget to run your ads campaign and Droparabia will take care of sourcing hundreds of different products for you and handle order fulfillment while you focus on scaling your business.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Dropshipping can be competitive, how do I succeed?<svg class="faq-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
            <p class="faq-body">Every single business model has competition. In order to succeed, you need to stand out as a whole unique brand, which very soon Droparabia will be able to help with through its laser machine that allows you to rebrand the products you sell.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Isn't it better to just start traditional e-commerce?<svg class="faq-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
            <p class="faq-body">A traditional e-commerce business requires at least $3000 to get started, not to mention searching for hours on Alibaba, buying a shipment of products you're not certain will sell, renting warehouses, paying fees... Droparabia does the research and product sourcing for you. You pay for each product you sell and keep the profit without managing any inventory — all with a small budget of $500.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>How much money can I make with Droparabia?<svg class="faq-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
            <p class="faq-body">It all depends on how much time and effort you're willing to invest. You're getting the same tools, guides and support as our +500 Lebanese users. Some are making $1k per month, some $700 in 2 weeks. How much you give to your business is how much you get.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>How long will it take to get started?<svg class="faq-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
            <p class="faq-body">Droparabia is designed to get you started in less than 30 days without all the headaches of researching and learning everything from scratch — a plug-and-play infrastructure to get your business launched as soon as possible.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>I don't have technical skills or marketing experience, can I succeed?<svg class="faq-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
            <p class="faq-body">That's exactly why we have a 5-day support team of advisors, MajdGBT our own AI assistant, and lots of free courses and recorded tutorials. We will build the website for you, teach you how to run ads and scale them, what tools to use to create your logo, how to use AI for content creation... Most of our users have barely any technical skills and still make the best use out of Droparabia.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>What if I don't get results?<svg class="faq-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
            <p class="faq-body">That's why we have a 90-day Money-Back Guarantee. If you use Droparabia correctly and follow our instructions and still didn't make a single sale in 90 days, you will get a full refund (after providing proof of your commitment to the platform and implementing instructions).</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Why start a dropshipping business under Lebanon's current situation?<svg class="faq-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
            <p class="faq-body">Droparabia's logistic network is located in a safe area away from the danger zone, meaning it's always taking orders and fulfilling them. Plus Droparabia sources from trusted suppliers outside Lebanon and local suppliers to make sure you always have something to sell.</p>
          </details>

        </div>
      </div>
